<i>dan menjadi terpuruk.</i>

00:36:10.264 --> 00:36:11.891
<i>Lalu aku melihat itu.</i>

00:36:13.059 --> 00:36:14.310
<i>Aku kehilangan kendali.</i>

00:36:14.393 --> 00:36:16.270
KOLEKSI NOH YOUNGJAE
