Hei, tunggu.

00:40:21.597 --> 00:40:22.682
- Aku?
- Ya.

00:40:23.516 --> 00:40:24.517
Polisi.

00:40:25.142 --> 00:40:26.143
Kau kenal Bae Jinkyu,

00:40:26.519 --> 00:40:27.561
bukan?

00:40:29.855 --> 00:40:31.107
Dia memulai bisnis.

00:40:32.066 --> 00:40:33.150
Bisnis macam apa?

00:40:33.609 --> 00:40:35.361
Entahlah.

00:40:35.528 --> 00:40:36.988
Dia masih merencanakannya.

00:40:37.113 --> 00:40:39.156
Katanya dia sudah menemukan investor.

00:40:40.324 --> 00:40:41.659
Kenapa?

00:40:45.079 --> 00:40:47.498
Ya. Aku ingat penumpang ini.

00:40:48.624 --> 00:40:50.167
Apa dia wanita?

00:40:52.336 --> 00:40:53.379
Kurasa bukan.

00:40:54.171 --> 00:40:55.464
Kau lihat wajahnya?

00:40:55.589 --> 00:40:56.590
Tidak.

00:40:56.674 --> 00:40:59.301
Dia menutupi wajah
dan menundukkan kepalanya.

00:41:00.886 --> 00:41:01.887
Bagaimana dia membayar?

00:41:01.971 --> 00:41:05.182
Dia membayar tunai
dan pergi tanpa ambil kembalian.

00:41:20.323 --> 00:41:22.074
Aku datang lagi.

00:41:24.702 --> 00:41:26.329
Bukankah direktur menghubungimu?

00:41:27.997 --> 00:41:29.498
Aku membeli kedua lukisan ini.

00:41:30.791 --> 00:41:32.126
Tolong tunggu sebentar...

00:41:32.501 --> 00:41:33.502
Baik.

00:41:35.880 --> 00:41:37.298
Ya, dia di sini.

00:41:40.634 --> 00:41:41.844
Baik, Bu.

00:41:42.553 --> 00:41:43.554
Baiklah.

